---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
const email = 'clement.cazaud@outlook.com';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Contact"
  description="Talk to Poesis about transformation, the Poesis stack, certification, or the GSM standard."
>
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="eyebrow">Contact</p>
      <h1>Let's talk.</h1>
      <p class="lead">Transformation engagements, the Poesis stack (SaaS or on-prem), certification, design partnerships, or the GSM standard — start the conversation.</p>
      <p style="margin-top:1.5rem"><a class="btn btn-primary" href={`mailto:${email}`}>Email us</a></p>
      <p class="muted" style="margin-top:1rem">Or join the conversation on <a href="https://github.com/orgs/poesis-cloud/discussions">GitHub Discussions</a>, browse the code on <a href="https://github.com/poesis-cloud">GitHub</a>, or follow us on <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/company/poesis-cloud">LinkedIn</a>.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section--soft">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="eyebrow">What to expect</p>
      <h2>A direct line to the people who built it.</h2>
      <p class="lead">Tell us your context and goal. We'll respond with the shortest credible path — and be honest if Poesis isn't the right fit yet.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="eyebrow">Join us</p>
      <h2>Help build the generative governance era.</h2>
      <p class="lead">Poesis is early, open, and ambitious. If you work on systemic governance, generative AI, enterprise architecture, or the kind of engineering that turns standards into running systems, we'd like to hear from you — even if there's no formal opening listed yet.</p>
      <p style="margin-top:1.5rem"><a class="btn btn-ghost" href={`mailto:${email}?subject=Joining%20Poesis`}>Introduce yourself →</a></p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
